{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idee27df8c-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s324"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"324"},"text":"§ 324.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Time, manner, etc., of annual payments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The sums appropriated by this subchapter to the States and Territories for the further endowment and support of colleges shall be annually paid on or before the 31st day of October of each year, by the Secretary of the Treasury, upon the warrant of the Secretary of Agriculture, out of the Treasury of the United States, to the State or Territorial treasurer, or to such officer as shall be designated by the laws of such State or Territory to receive the same, who shall, upon the order of the trustees of the college, or the institution for colored students, immediately pay over said sums to the treasurers of the respective colleges or other institutions entitled to receive the same, and such treasurers shall be required to report to the Secretary of Agriculture, on or before the 1st day of December of each year, a detailed statement of the amount so received and of its disbursement. The grants of moneys authorized by this subchapter are made subject to the legislative assent of the several States and Territories to the purpose of said grants.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idee27df8d-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1890-08-30/ch841/s2"},"text":"Aug. 30, 1890, ch. 841, § 2","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/26/418"},"text":"26 Stat. 418","children":[],"tail":"; 1939 Reorg. Plan No. I, §§ 201, 204, eff. "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1939-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 1939","children":[],"tail":", 4 F.R. 2728, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/53/1424"},"text":"53 Stat. 1424","children":[],"tail":"; 1953 Reorg. Plan No. 1, §§ 5, 8, eff. "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1953-04-11"},"text":"Apr. 11, 1953","children":[],"tail":", 18 F.R. 2053, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/67/631"},"text":"67 Stat. 631","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/273/s9/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–273, § 9(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1976-04-21"},"text":"Apr. 21, 1976","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/90/378"},"text":"90 Stat. 378","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/88/tIII/s301/a/2/E"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–88, title III, § 301(a)(2)(E)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1979-10-17"},"text":"Oct. 17, 1979","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/93/677"},"text":"93 Stat. 677","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/98/tXIV/s1419"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–98, title XIV, § 1419","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1981-12-22"},"text":"Dec. 22, 1981","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/95/1306"},"text":"95 Stat. 1306","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idee27df8e-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idee27df8f-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idee27df90-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1976—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/273"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–273","children":[],"tail":" substituted “October” for “July” and “December” for “September”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idee27df91-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"transferOfFunctions","id":"idee27df92-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Transfer of Functions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For transfer of functions under this section to Secretary of Agriculture, see note set out under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s321"},"text":"section 321 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Functions of Department of Health, Education, and Welfare and Secretary thereof under this subchapter transferred to Secretary of Education by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/88/s301/a/2/E"},"text":"section 301(a)(2)(E) of Pub. L. 96–88","children":[],"tail":", which is classified to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s3441/a/2/E"},"text":"section 3441(a)(2)(E) of Title 20","children":[],"tail":", Education."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Transfer of functions from Secretary of the Interior to Secretary of Health, Education, and Welfare, see note set out under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s321"},"text":"section 321 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
